	(text "If operating from a single supply, use a 22-Ω resistor in\nseries with the VDD supply line and a 1-μF low ESR capacitor \nto filter any power supply noise. The previous capacitor \nplacement considerations apply. However note that\nwhere LED current is boosted beyond 100mA, it is \nrecommended that the LEDA pin be connected to a separate\npower supply. "
		(exclude_from_sim no)
